title: Mother in Law, apartment
posting_body: ['I am completing construction on what will soon be a brand new apartment / MIL in a farmhouse in Fall City.', ' The main part of the house is occupied', 'but this is a lovely basement apartment with fireplace, full bath, 2 bedrooms, kitchen.', ' All new.', ' There is good light from windows and very spacious.', ' 1,000 square feet.', ' It is on 1.5 acres that is shared with the occupants of the main floor.', ' Lovely garden area.', 'Ideal tenant will want to participate in what the yard and property offers.', ' Walking distance to downtown Fall City.', 'This is a rare opportunity and will not last long so even though it is not finished yet I hope to provide advance notice to find the perfect tenant.', '5 minutes from I-90.', ' 15-20 minutes to Redmond.']
